14 SUMMARY
1155 This amendment replaces the bill, which is a concept draft, with a resolve. The
1166 amendment appropriates funds to the Department of Education to continue the early
1177 literacy grant program and grant programming related to implementation of best practices
1188 for mathematics instruction in schools. The amendment authorizes the department to
1199 partner with a national foundation to maximize private resources.
